title: E-Racer [Cool Racing Game]

PC-GAME.....: E-Racer
Publisher...: Rage Software
Developer...: Rage Software
Platform....: PC / Windows
Genre.......: Driving/Racing 

Description 
This racing game, for single or multiple players, uses the latest
3D technologies to deliver the ultimate racing experience.
Played offline, users can enter races and refine their skills
with a range of highly tuned vehicles on challenging race tracks.
Then you can go online and join other players in competitions,
join teams and download new tracks or cars, and view championship
standings, best lap times, and other statistics.

Installation.
Unzip E-Racer
Mount images to virtual drive that support
Compressed .daa images. (PowerISO) or burn
to disk.
 
Read INFO.nfo (in notepad) then
play and have fun.
